    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你对体育了解多少？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用最受欢迎的运动来测试你的知识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sports Trivia Challenge 从未如此有趣。你可以在单人模式中挑战自己，也可以在派对模式（最多4人）与亲友来一场体育问答之夜。选择类别，回答数千道四选一题目。想要更刺激？转动 Wheel Challenge！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收录 9 大粉丝最爱类别：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Baseball</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basketball</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Football</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hockey</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>General</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Olympics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sports Records</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tennis</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>World Cup</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人模式</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>派对模式（最多 4 名玩家）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数千道四选一题目</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适合团体问答之夜</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速、即开即玩</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全家都能一起玩的体育问答</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>支持手柄</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还等什么？立即下载，让大脑进入 The Sports Trivia Challenge 状态！</p>",
